testCase.title: Perform register operation with valid credentials
steps: Register a new account using valid and complete input fields (e.g., unique email, strong password)
testCase.successCriteria: Account is successfully created, user is redirected or shown a success message, and no backend or frontend errors appear.

notes: Like I said add a data privacy notice or terms and conditions checkbox during registering to let users know how their data is being used.
